<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   `Scarlett: the Sequel' Rights
   For TV Are Sold to Halmi
   ----
   A Wall Street Journal News Roundup
</HL>
<DATE>
11/04/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B2
</SO>
<CO>
   CBS
</CO>
